{"tid":1338322,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"前和理非嘅p牌發問","createTime":"2019-07-21T13:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T13:55:26.000Z","uid":264013,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"024060d6464b6f3a4884a230bb61ff8dde7a6848","tid":1338322,"uid":264013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"小弟衣家都係半個勇武la，頭先見到啲嘢唔係好明<br />\n話說 香港站e出口對出行多幾步有個隧道口<span style=\"color: blue;\">由於唔係住嗰度之前遊行又冇行到咁入所以唔知叫咩名</span><br />\nbtw本身應該封咗路冇lala有車由隧道出嚟<br />\n帶頭司機落左車同隧道口嘅兄弟發生口角一開始都冇乜嘢有啲肢體碰撞，基本嘢la<br />\n但該名司機突然返回車上本以為已經平息但該車突然洗前差啲撞到我哋嘅人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我位置唔好有邊個睇得清楚啲請幫我補充plz</span></span><br />\n仲有，大家都見到我係p牌真係唔係好識規矩有咩唔啱任屌！"},{"pid":"7c95c2b4c64db8314ee4410aaf6e2d22837346e4","tid":1338322,"uid":264013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"自推倒數10<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d51c067a0262cc5d3b5c92be85f5b5af25ddb1","tid":1338322,"uid":264013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"自推倒數9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3320c1293e89f4b8e62938d7a719ac3a8abf3ab7","tid":1338322,"uid":264013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"自推倒數8<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09e0dbeefdc3de1754b9bdd2ba62dc58927d914","tid":1338322,"uid":264013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"自推倒數7<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class